<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM9.5.5">
<l>tiṇṭimi lēṟṟiṉma ṇiyumāyaṉ tīṅkuḻa lōcaiyum teṉṟalōṭu</l>
<l>koṇṭatōr mālaiyu mantiyīṉṟa kōlavi ḷampiṟai yōṭukūṭi</l>
<l>paṇṭaiya vallavi vainamakkup pāviyē ṉāviyai vāṭṭañceyyum</l>
<l>koṇṭalmaṇi niṟavaṇ ṇarmaṉṉu kuṟuṅkuṭik kēyeṉṉai yuyttiṭumiṉ.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The bells on the bulls with thick humps, the sound of a herder’s sweet flute,</l>
<l>The evening’s bearing of the southern breeze, and the lovely, young crescent</l>
<l rend="indent">that dusk begets, all together,</l>
<l>These are not as before for us! They create anguish for my soul,</l>
<l rend="indent">wretched me.</l>
<l>Make sure you take me to Kuṟuṅkuṭi where dwells the one</l>
<l rend="indent">the hue of sapphire [and] clouds.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
